  Ho2-taN2 bo5 kiaN e5 Lou5-ui 
  Siong7-te3 sou2 heng-khi2 lai5 soan-thoan5 I e5 oe7 ti7 ko-san-chok8 e5 te7-ji7 e5 leng2-siu3, chiu7-si7 chit8 ui7 e5 chheng-lian5 kio3-cho3 Lou5-ui. Chha-put-to ti7 1928 ni5, tng i iau2 cho3 chit8 mia5 e5 hok8-bu7-seng ti7 Hoe-lian5-kang2 hu7-kun7 e5 keng2-chhat-sou2 teh hok8-bu7 e5 si5, bat khoaN3-tioh8 hia e5 han3-jin5 kau3-hoe7 e5 pou3-to7-thoan5 teh pou3-to7, chiu7 oa2 khi3 thiaN. I chek-si5 tui3 hok-im siN-khi2 heng3-chhu3, chiu7 khi3 chham-ka hia e5 Seng3-keng-pan; hit pan si7 chit8 ui7 lu2 thoan5-to7 kio3-cho3 Iau5--si7 U7 (peng5-siong5 lang5 kio3 i cho3 U7-a2) teh leng2-to7 e5. I khi3 ka-jip8 Seng3-keng-pan si7 ui7-tioh8 ai3 chai-iaN2 chit e5 ki5-iN7 e5 to7-li2 khah siong5-se3 e5 in-toaN. Lu2 thoan5-to7 chiu7 chiong i sou2 bat e5 to7-li2 chin7 thoan5 hou7 i; chong2-si7 i e5 sim-koaN kap leng5-hun5 iau2 kam2-kak bo5 moa2-chiok. I chiu7 ka7 i kong2, Na7 e7 tit thang tit-tioh8 keng2-chhat e5 un2-chun2, li2 koh khi3 Tam7-chui2 gian2-kiu3, in-ui7 u7 chit8 keng Ka-na2-tai7 Soan-to7-hoe7 e5 Sin5-hak8-hau7 ti7 hia. Chiau3 i sou2 u7-liau7 e5 khoan2, keng2-chhat ko2-jian5 khiok-ha7 i e5 sin-chheng2, m7-chun2 i li7-khui soaN-te7, chong2-si7 i iah8 bo5 ui7-tioh8 an2-ni lai5 sit-bang7. Chit ui7 ho2-taN2 e5 chheng-lian5, chiu7 bo5 siu7 keng2-chhat e5 hu2-kho2 thau chau2, kap i e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 khi3 kau3 Tam7-chui2, iah8 kiu5 Sun Bok8-su tioh8 chiap-lap8 in. 
  Sun Bok8-su chai-iaN2 in chit khoan2 e5 iau-kiu5, kiam2-chhai2 si7 i e5 ki5-to2 e5 in3 siaN; in-ui7 i u7 ki5-to2, ng3-bang7 hok-im oe7 thang thoan5 jip8 ti7 ko-san-chok8 e5 tiong-kan; chiu7 chiap-lap8 in, piaN3 lau5-kha hou7 in toa3, iah8 ui7-tioh8 Lou5-ui kap te3 boe2-au7 koh kau3 e5 kui2-na7 lang5 siat tek8-piat8 e5 kho3-theng5 hou7 in thang thak8. Lou5-ui u7 eng7 boe7 soe-the3 e5 jiat8-seng5 gian2-kiu3 Seng3-keng nng7 ni5 khah ke ku2, to7-li2 chiam7-chiam7 beng5-liau5. Siong7-te3 e5 chin-li2 u7 chiong i lak8-tiau5--teh, Siong7-te3 e5 chi2-i3 u7 kai2-cho7 i e5 sim kap jin5-keh, che si7 cheng3-lang5 sou2 chai-iaN2 e5. I chiu7 kong-jian5 ko3-pek8 i tui3 Ki-tok e5 sin3-giong2, siu7 se2-le2; tng2-khi3 ti7 Thai3-ia5-chok8 e5 tiong-kan lai5 cho3 kang. 
  I beh tng2-khi3 e5 si5, Jit8-pun2 e5 koaN-hian3 chiu7 keng2-ko3 i kong2, “M7-chun2 li2 thoan5 Ki-tok-kau3 hou7 lin2 ka-ki7 e5 peh-siN3. Goan2 u7 teh ka7 in chun2-pi7 chit8 khoan2 e5 chong-kau3, chiu7-si7 beh ka3 in pai3 sin5-to7 (sin5-to7 a2-si7 kong2 sin5-sia7 chiu7-si7 Jit8-pun2 lang5 pai3 sin5 e5 hong-hoat).” M7-ku2 Thai3-ia5-chok8 goan5-lai5 chiu7-si7 boe7 bat khut-hok8 lang5 e5 peh-siN3, ia7 Lou5-ui chiu7-si7 hit e5 chin-chiaN3 tian2-heng5-tek e5 jin5-but8. In-ui7 i2-keng koat-sim beh thoan5-to7, i chiu7 ku7-choat8, bo5 beh chun-siu2 chit ho7 e5 beng7-leng7. I chiu7 tng2-khi3 soaN-nih hong2-bun7 chhin-chiaN5 kap peng5-iu2, tui3 in kong2-khi2 i sou2 tit-tioh8 sin e5 sin3-giong2, iah8 ti7 in e5 ke-nih thoan5-to7. I chai-iaN2 kong-jian5 ui5-keh8 koaN-leng7 si7 gu5-gong7, chiu7 theng3-hau7 kau3 poaN3-mi5 au7 chiah pi3-bit8 lai5 khui-hoe7. Kui2 geh8-jit8 au7, soan-kau3-su u7 thiaN-tioh8 hong-siaN, iah8 u7 chiap-tioh8 kan3-chiap-tek e5 siau-sit kong2, Lou5-ui i2-keng chu7-chip8 chha-put-to saN-chap8 mia5 e5 sin3-chia2, chun2-pi7 beh nia2 se2-le2. Bo5 lang5 oe7 tit thang jip8 khi3 hia cheng3-beng5 hit e5 siau-sit, put-ko3 Jit8-pun2 e5 Seng3-keng u7 ti7 am3-chiN7 e5 tiong-kan theh8 jip8-khi3 Thai3-ia5-chok8 e5 te7-thau5, ng3-bang7 hiah-e5 Seng3-keng oe7 thang chhiok-chin3 hok-im e5 chin3-tian2. 
  An2-ni hit e5 un7-tong7 u7 hoat-tian2 chin kin2. Ni5-lau7 e5 Chi-oang2 ti7 tang-hai2-hoaN7 Hoe-lian5-kang2 chiu-ui5 teh kang-chok e5 tiong-kan, chheng-lian5 e5 Lou5-ui u7 chiong i e5 lou7-theng5 phah khah khui, chin3-jip8 kau3 tiong-iong soaN-meh8 e5 sou2-chai7. Chiong hok-im chit8-sia7 thoan5 koe3 chit8-sia7. Chit ui7 Ki-tok e5 su3-chia2 chiu7 liam5-piN kiaN5-thau3 Thai3-ia5-chok8 e5 choan5 te7-khu, iah8 u7 cho7-chiu7 kui2-na7 thoan5 e5 sin3-tou5 san3-chai7 ti7 khui-khoah e5 te7-hng. (Na7 khoaN3 te7-tou5 chiu7 chai-iaN2 u7 chit8 tiau5 soaN-kok chiong tiong-iong soaN-meh8 kap hai2-hoaN7 e5 cheng3 soaN keh-khui, hit tiau5 soaN-kok chiu7-si7 tui3 Hoe-lian5-kang2 tit8 thau3 loh8 lam5 kau3 Tai5-tang e5, iah8 u7 chit8 tiau5 thih-lou7 cho7 thau3-koe3. Lou5-ui kang-chok chu2-iau3 e5 hoan7-ui5 si7 tiau3-oan2 e5 soaN-te7, chiu7-si7 Hoe-lian5-kang2 e5 sai-pak; Chi-oang2 sou2 kau3 e5 sou2-chai7 chiu7-si7 hoe2-chhia lou7-piN, chiu7-si7 pi2-kau3-tek khah khoai3 kau3 e5 sou2-chai7.) 
  U7 chit8 jit8, keng2-chhat ti7 chit8 ui7 Thai3-ia5-chok8 e5 ke-nih khoaN3-tioh8 chit8 pun2 Seng3-keng. Chit e5 hoat-kian3 u7 jia2-khi2 toa7 kiaN-hiaN5 kap heng-hun3. Keng2-chhat chiu7 ti7 hit e5 choan5 te7-hng chin3-heng5 liau2 chit8 chhu3 e5 toa7 sou-cha, ng3-bang7 thang tit-tioh8 tak8 ho7 bun5 e5 Seng3-keng kap si-chheh. Chong2-si7 ti7 am3-chiN7 e5 tiong-kan toa3-jip8 soaN-te7 e5 Seng3-keng it-hoat na2 ke-thiN; iu7-koh chiah-e5 Seng3-keng na7 u7 kui2 pun2 siu7 hoat-kian3-tioh8, hiah-e5 siu7 hoat-kian3-tioh8 e5 Thai3-ia5-chok8 e5 ka-teng5 tak8 e5 long2 tiau3 khi3 keng2-chhat-sou2, kong3 kau3 ka-chiah-phiaN huih chim-chim lau5. Keng2-chhat u7 kiong5-pek in tioh8 pang3-sak Ki-tok-kau3, na7-si7 in in3 kong2, “Lin2 oe7 thang chiau3 lin2 sou2 ai3 cham7-tng7 goan2 e5 kha-chhiu2, chong2-si7 goan2 e5 sim goan5-chai7 si7 Ki-tok-tou5 e5 sim.” 
  Chit e5 tai7-chi3 chiu7-si7 ti7 1938 ni5, Jit8-pun2 kap Tiong-kok khai-chian3 boe7 loa7-ku2 e5 si5 sou2 tu2-tioh8--e5. (Jit8-pun2 kap Tiong-kok khai-chian3 si7 1937 ni5 7 geh8). Ui7-tioh8 beh i5-chhi5 chian3-si5 to7-tek, Jit8-pun2 e5 tong-kiok8-chia2 u7 chou2-chit chit8 e5 phou2-pian3-tek e5 “cheng-sin5 chong2-tong7-oan5 un7-tong7.” Ui7-tioh8 beh chhiok-chin3 ai3-kok-sim ti7 Tai5-oan5 lang5 e5 tiong-kan, in sou2 eng7 koe3 e5 hong-hoat e5 chit8 hang7, chiu7-si7 phoe3-hoat sin5-kham (kamidana) ti7 kok ka-teng5-nih. Hit e5 lun7-tiam2, si7 kong2 chit khoan2 e5 sin5-kham si7 kap kok-ki5 kang7 khoan2, piN5-piN5 si7 chit8 chiong2 ai3-kok-sim e5 piau2-hian7. Chong2-si7 chai7 toa7-to-sou3 e5 Jit8-pun2 lang5 lai5 kong2, chit e5 khak-sit8 u7 chong-kau3-tek i3-gi7 ti7-teh. Chong2 kong2, keng2-chhat put-tan3 beng7-leng7 kok ka-teng5 tioh8 boe2 chit8 e5 sin5-kham, koh iah8 teh khoaN3 lang5 u7 eng7 chiau3-khi2-kang e5 keng3-khian5 tui3-thai7 i a2-bo5? Lian5 hiah-e5 kho2-lin5 e5 ko-san-chok8 iah8 u7 siu7-tioh8 chit ho7 sin5-kham e5 phoe3-hoat. Sit8-chai7 lai5 kong2, Chit khoan2 thang gi7-lun7 e5 sip8-siok8, i2-keng u7 jia2-khi2 siong-tong e5 phaiN2 kam2-cheng5; ia7 keng2-chhat chai-iaN2 chit e5 si5-chun7 si7 tioh8 eng7 “nng2-ap” e5 si5-chun7. TaN, kap Tiong-kok e5 chian3-tou3 i2-keng khai-si2, in khak-sit8 bo5 ai3 koh kiau2-jiau2 hiah-e5 ko-san-chok8 lah. In m7-ai3 goa7-kok e5 chong-kau3 lai5 kam2-hoa3 hiah-e5 lang5, iah8 kiaN-kiN3 na7 siuN koe3-tou7 ap-pek Ki-tok-tou5, oe7 cho7-chiaN5 it-poaN e5 put-an, iah8 ti7 ko-san-chok8 e5 tiong-kan u7 hoat-seng toa7 hoan2-loan7 e5 kho2-leng5-seng3 ti7-teh. 
  Hiah-e5 u7 Seng3-keng e5 lang5 sui-jian5 u7 ku7-choat8, m7-goan7 poe7-kau3, iau2-ku2 tu5-khi3 in e5 leng2-siu3 Lou5-ui chit8 lang5 siu7 koaiN i2-goa7, long2 siu7 thau2-pang3 tng2-khi3 soaN-nih. Tu5-khi3 chiong Ki-tok-kau3 thoan5-po3 ti7 ko-san-chok8 i2-goa7, keng2-chhat u7 ko3 i mou7-tok8 sin5-kham, chiu7-si7 phoe3-ti3 ti7 i e5 ke-nih e5. I tui3 hit e5 sin5-kham bo5 piau2 keng3-i3, iah8 bo5 ka7 i pai3; i khak-sit8 u7 eng7 i lai5 cho3 chit8 kha siuN-a2 teh te2 phoe! Lou5-ui e5 siu7-liah8 kap siu7 koaiN e5 su7, u7 jia2-khi2 boe7 kau3 loa7 sio2 e5 jiau2-tong7. Te3 i e5 lang5 u7 chit8 toa7 tin7 khi3 keng2-chhat-sou2, toa7 hoat phi5-khi3 kong2, “Lou5-ui na7-si7 ui7-tioh8 cho3 Ki-tok-tou5 e5 su7 lai5 siu7 koaiN, goan2 tai7-ke iah8 long2 si7 Ki-tok-tou5. TaN tioh8 chaiN2-iuN7?” Chong2-si7 keng2-chhat ku7-choat8, m7-ai3 kap in pian7-lun7, iah8 kin2-sin7 m7-ai3 chiong su7 bu2-long7 khah toa7. 
  Tong-kiok8-chia2 kiam2-chhai2 siuN7 kong2, na7 chiong chhiong3-siu2-chia2 Lou5-ui chit8 lang5 ka7 i tu5-tiau7, hit e5 un7-tong7 chiu7 liam5-piN siau-biat8; chong2-si7 che si7 chin toa7 e5 chho3-gou7. Lou5-ui i2-keng loah hoe2; hit e5 hoe2-iam7 taN si7 boe7 tit thang phah-hoa lah. Iau2-ku2 ti7 hit e5 si5-chun7 bo5 lang5 oe7 thang tai7-seng chai-iaN2 beh tu2-tioh8 siaN2-su7. Ti7 1940 ni5 e5 ni5-boe2, soan-kau3-su thiat-the3 e5 si5, in sou2 chai-iaN2--e5, chiu7-si7 Lou5-ui i2-keng siu7 koaiN chha-put-to nng7 ni5 ku2, iah8 u7 hoan7-tioh8 kha-khi3-piN7 e5 su7. I e5 sin-khu bian2 kong2 si7 ti7 thih-thang e5 lai7-bin7, chong2-si7 i e5 cheng-sin5 teh kiaN5-iu5 ti7 hiah-e5 cheng3 soaN-kan, ia7 i e5 oe7 iau2-ku2 teh tin2-tang7 ti7 i tong5-pau e5 sim-nih. Pat8 lang5 u7 ke3-siok8 i sou2 khai-si2 e5 kang-chok. Hit e5 ni5-lau7 e5 Chi-oang2 iau2-ku2 ti7 tang-hai2-hoaN7 teh chit8-chiuN7 chit8-loh8, iah8 ti7 khui-khoah e5 te7-khu kap cheng3 Ki-tok-tou5 teh chiap-chhiok. Hiah-e5 khia7-khi2 ti7 soaN-kan e5 Ki-tok-tou5, chiu7-si7 tui3 Lou5-ui e5 in2-chhoa7 lai5 jip8 sin3--e5, na7 u7 su-iau3 e5 si5 oe7 thang kap i chiap-hiap8. Ti7 chit ho7 e5 khou2-keng2 tiong, in e5 un7-tong7 iau2-ku2 hoat8-phoat teh chin3-tian2. Che si7 Siong7-te3 e5 Sin5 kap in ti7-teh, ui7-tioh8 I pun2-sin e5 eng5-kng kek8-lek8 teh kang-chok, che si7 boe7 hou2-jin7-tit e5 su7-sit8; na7 li7-khui chit e5 su7-sit8, tai7-chi3 chiu7 boe7-tit thang soat-beng5. Chit e5 su7-sit8 oe7 eng7-tit eng7 “I chhoa7 in chhut” chit si3-ji7 lai5 piau2-hian7. Chhoa7 in li7-khui chho3-gou7 kap be5-sin3 e5 ou-am3, lai5 jip8 ti7 I ki5-biau7 e5 kng-beng5 e5 chiu7-si7 Siong7-te3. 
  Lou5-ui u7 eng7 thang o-lo2 e5 un-khun5 kap bin2-chiat8 lai5 oan5-seng5 hit e5 “Siong7-teng2-siong7 e5 kang.” I u7 ti7 hit e5 hiam2-iau3 e5 te7-tiam2 pang3 hoe2 sio soaN-phiaN5, sin3-sok koh bin2-chiat8, ia7 chit-chun7 i u7 chiong hoe2-pe2 kau-koe3 pat8 lang5 e5 chhiu2, thang lai5 oan5-seng5 chit e5 kang; in-ui7 Siong7-te3 ti7 i boe7 chhek-tok8-tit e5 ti3-hui7-nih, u7 hou7 I sou2 keng2-soan2 chit e5 khi3-ku7 siu7-tioh8 chit8 cham7 koaiN-kaN e5 kan-khou2. Chhi3 siuN7 chit ui7 giam2-ngi7 e5 ko-san chu7-bin5, ti7 i sim-nih u7 soaN-tiuN5 e5 tiau3-beng7, ia7 siu7 bian2-kiong2 lai5 ong2-hui3 chhit ni5 ku2 e5 kong-im ti7 Jit8-pun2 e5 kaN-gak8-nih! I kiam2 u7 chhin-chhiuN7 siu7 liah8 e5 eng-chiau2, a2-si7 sim2-mih8 ia2-chiau2 ui7-tioh8 beh chong5-chhut--lai5, thi2-khui i e5 sit8 lai5 phiat8 hit e5 chiau2-lang mah? Na7 u7 iaN2 an2-ni lai5 kong2, chit phiN e5 te5-su5 tioh8 oaN7 cho3 “Sit-chi3 e5 Lou5-ui,” a2-si7 “Sit-pai7-chia2 Lou5-ui.” Chong2-si7 su7-sit8 i bo5 an2-ni! Sui-jian5 ti7 kaN-nih, i iah8 si7 thun-lun2, kah na2 chhin-chhiuN7 teh khoaN3 hit ui7 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 e5 Siong7-te3. 
  Siong7-te3 bo5 pang3-sak i, I bo5 boe7 ki3-tit Lou5-ui, iah8 bo5 boe7 ki3-tit i e5 tong5-pau, chiu7-si7 ti7 soaN-kan ui7-tioh8 sin3-giong2 teh siu7 pek-hai7 e5. Siong7-te3 ti7 ho2 e5 si5-ki chhoah-tng7 pak8 in e5 soh. 1945 ni5 Jit8-pun2 tau5-hang5 e5 si5, Lou5-ui siu7 thau2-pang3 tng2-khi3 tang hai2-hoaN7 lai5 hok8-to3 i thoan5 hok-im e5 kang. I u7 khoaN3-tioh8 ti7 i bo5 ti7-teh e5 tiong-kan chit8-chng koe3 chit8 chng e5 ko-san-chok8 i2-keng piN3-chiaN5 cho3 Ki-tok-tou5 lah. TaN in m7-bian2 koh ti7 pi3-bit8 tiong lai5 chu7-hoe7, in kong-jian5 ko3-peh8 sin3-giong2, iah8 khi2 tek e5 pai3-tng5 lai5 hok8-sai7 tok8-it chin e5 Siong7-te3. I hoaN-hi2 khoaN3 Siong7-te3 chaiN2-iuN7 chin2-kiu3 I e5 peh-siN3 thoat-chhut ou-am3 e5 koan5-se3, lai5 jip8 ti7 I thiaN3 kiaN2 e5 kok. Siong7-te3 e5 oe7 bo5 lok8-khong. Toa7-soaN kap sio2-soaN i2-keng khui chhui3 teh chhiuN3-koa. 
  1946 ni5 e5 chhun-thiN, soan-kau3-su siu7 un2-chun2 tng2-lai5 kau3 Tai5-oan5. Sun Sian-siN chin7-liong7 koaN2-kin2 khi2-sin khi3 tang hai2-hoaN7 lai5 khoaN3 hiah-e5 ko-san-chok8 tau3-ti2 an2-choaN2 koe3-jit8, (in-ui7 chian3-cheng tiong in bo5 chiap-tioh8 Tai5-oan5 e5 siau-sit. I siong5-siong5 teh sam3-su kong2, “TaN hiah-e5 pi3-bit8 siu7 kam3-si7 e5 lang5 m7-chai an2-choaN2?” I iah8 siong5-siong5 thoe3 in ki5-to2, kiu5 Siong7-te3 na7 oe7 choe3--tit, tioh8 ti7 keng2-chhat bu5-to7 e5 ap-pek ha7 jiau5-lau5 in e5 siN3-mia7 kau3 kin-a2-jit8). Keng-ke3 chit8 jit8 thiam2-thiam2 e5 lou7-cham7, i ti7 poaN3-mi5 nng7 tiam2 kau3 Hoe-lian5-kang2, i2-keng chiah8 chit8 oaN2 png7, chiu7 khi3 khun3. Khun3 kau3 lak8 tiam2 e5 si5, Lou5-ui u7 lai5 kio3-chhiN2 i e5 bin5. Che chai7 Sun Sian-siN e5 lip8-tiuN5 lai5 kong2, si7 chit8 kiaN7 oan5-choan5 bo5 phai3-phe e5 gong5-ngiah8 i2-kip8 thang hoaN-hi2 e5 su7. 
  Sun Sian-siN sia2 kong2, “Goa2 oe7 thang koh kiN3-tioh8 i e5 bin7 si7 heng7-hok,” koh ke-thiN chit8 ku3 kong2, “I hian7-si5 choan-sim teh cho3 kau3-hoe7 e5 kang, teh in2-chhoa7 kang2 chheng e5 tong5-pau lai5 kui Ki-tok.” Lan2 boe7-tit-thang hiam5 i kong2 liau2 khah koe3-thau5. 
  Ui2-lan5 e5 kian3-cheng3 
  Ui2-lan5 chiu7-si7 Thai3-ia5-chok8 tiong kiat8-chhut e5 jin5-but8. I khia7-khi2 ti7 Eng-hoa chhoan. Eng-hoa chhoan si7 ti7 Leng5-ko soaN-kok koh khi2-khi3 e5 sou2-chai7, li7 Hoe-lian5-kang2 sio2-khoa2 u7 hiah hng7. I ti7 1938 ni5 tui3 Chi-oang2 thiaN-tioh8 to7-li2, chiu7 ti7 hit sia7-nih chiaN5-cho3 thau5 chit8 e5 Ki-tok-tou5. I chiu7 liam5-piN tui3 i e5 chhin-chhek kap peng5-iu2 siN-khi2 koan-sim, chiu7 khoan3-iu2 chit8 thoan5 e5 lang5 cheng3-sek kap i choe3 tin7 khi3 Ka-le2-oan Chi-oang2 hia (saN-li7 15 eng-li2). In ti7 hia tui3 Seng3-keng u7 tit-tioh8 ke chin3 chit8 pou7 e5 ka3-si7. 1941 ni5 4 geh8, u7 chit8 mi5-hng tng in chu7-chip8 ti7 hia teh gian2-kiu3 Seng3-keng e5 si5, keng2-chhat hut-jian5-kan jip8-lai5 hit keng chhu3, chiong chhut-sek8 e5 lang5-mia5 long2 cho3 chit8-e7 ki3-ki3 khi3. Kui2-jit8 au7, in chiu7 hou7 in tiau3 khi3 keng2-chhat-sou2 siu7 sim2-mng7. Keng2-chhat u7 phah lai5 sim2-mng7 in, leng5-ti7 in, chiau-that in, hi3-lang7 in, iah8 kah in tioh8 gim5-si hou7 in thiaN, choe3-au7 Ui2-lan5 chit8 lang5 u7 siu7 phah kau3 thiam2-thiam2. Tui3 hit-tiap8 i2-au7, keng2-chhat tui3 hiah-e5 ko-san-chok8 e5 sin3-tou5 su7-su7 to m7 hoaN-hi2. Ui2-lan5 kap toa3 ti7 Eng-hoa chhoan e5 thoan5-the2 tioh8 kau3 poaN3-ni5 au7 chiah kaN2 khui pi3-bit8 e5 chip8-hoe7. Che si7 beh siam2-pi7 cheng-tham3, kiaN-liau2 hou7 in khoaN3--tioh8 chiu7 beh chau2-khi3 po3. 
  1943 ni5, u7 chit8 mi5-hng, keng2-chhat chiap-tioh8 in teh chu7-hoe7 e5 siau-sit, chiu7 chhim-jip8 in e5 hoe7-tiuN5, lai5 but8-siu in long2-chong2 e5 Seng3-keng. Keh tng2-jit8 hiah-e5 chham-ka chu7-hoe7 e5 long2 tiau3 khi3 Hoe-lian5-kang2 keng2-chhat-kiok8, ti7 hia tui3 Iu2-tian5 (Tomoda) hu3 chu2-jim7 siu7-tioh8 chit8 tiuN5 chin khok-heng5 e5 sim2-mng7. Hit lang5 me7 in kong2, in pai3 “Bi2-kok lang5 e5 Siong7-te3.” Hit-tiap8 i2-au7 ui7-tioh8 beh kiam2-chio2 siu7 cheng-tham3 e5 gui5-hiam2, Eng-hoa chhoan e5 Ki-tok-tou5 chiu7 chiong in e5 chu7-hoe7 hun cho3 saN e5 thoan5-the2. Sui-jian5 siu7-tioh8 keng2-chhat chin kek-liat8 e5 ap-che3, in e5 lang5-giah8 iah8 si7 goan5-chai7 teh ke-thiN. Ui7-tioh8 beh siam2-pi7 lang5 e5 giau5-gi5, in ti7 le2-pai3-jit8 chheng7 kang-chok-hok8 (cho3 kang teh chheng7 e5 saN) chhut-khi3. Keng2-chhat si7 siuN7 kong2, in kaN2 beh khi3 hng5-nih cho3 kang, na7-si7 su7-sit8 in si7 beh khi3 soaN-nih cho3-hoe2 le2-pai3. 
  Sio-siang7 hit ni5, Ui2-lan5 u7 koh chit8 pai2 siu7 tiau3 kau3 keng2-chhat e5 bin7-cheng5, siu7 ko3-sou3, kong2 i u7 soan-thoan5 ok-seng3 e5 oe7. U7 lang5 kan-cheng3 i, kong2 i bat kong2-khi2 Jip8-pun2 beh thai5 su Bi2-kok, iah8 Tai5-oan5 e5 Ki-tok-tou5 beh siu7 kai2-hong3. Ui7-tioh8 beh kiong5-pek i lai5 chiau3-sit8 kong2, hit mi5-hng u7 nng7 e5 keng2-chhat phah Ui2-lan5, phah kau3 si2-si2 hun7-hun7--khi3. In theng5 chhiu2 hioh-khun3 chit8 tiap-a2-ku2, hit e5 kio3-cho3 Tsubaki e5 keng2-tiuN2 chiu7 mng7 i, khoaN3 i beh poe7-kau3 a2 m7; na7-si7 Ui2-lan5 ku7-choat8 kong2, i boe7-tit-thang pang3-sak hok-im. Keng2-chhat chiu7 kong3 i e5 thau5-khak, hou7 i hun7--loh8-khi3. In liah8 cho3 i kaN2 i2-keng hou7 in phah-si2, chiu7 ka7 i hiat-kak8 ti7 keng2-chhat-sou2 goa7. U7 chit8 ui7 Eng-hoa chhoan e5 chheng-lian5 sin3-tou5 chiong i aiN7 tng2-khi3 in tau. I ti7 chhu3-nih nng7-jit8 ku2 to2-teh, long2 m7-chai lang5; i e5 ka chok8 jiat8-chhiat thoe3 i ki5-to2, ng3-bang7 i oe7 koh hoe5 hun5. Ti7 te7-saN jit8, i chiu7 peh khi2-lai5. Tu2-chiah kam2-kak oe7 koh khi2-lai5 kiaN5 na7-tiaN7, chiu7 ke3-ek8 beh khi3 Hoe-lian5-kang2 kau3-hoe7, chong2-si7 ti7 lou7-nih u7 hou7 keng2-chhat kio3 jip8-khi3 keng2-chhat-sou2. Chit hoe5 keng2-tiuN2 ka7 i kong2, in bo5 an3-sng3 beh phah i, chong2-si7 u7 chit8 hang7, ai3 i tioh8 koaN2-kin2 ka7 in kong2, chiu7-si7 Bi2-kok si7 an2-choaN2 teh ke3-ek8 beh ti7 Tai5-oan5 siong7-liok8, soa3 kai2-hong3 Ki-tok-tou5 e5 su7. Ui2-lan5 ka7 i kong2, i m7 chai-iaN2 chit chan5 su7, keng2-chhat chiu7 in3 kong2, “Ho2! ho2! beh chit8 le2-pai3 ku2 hou7 li2 bo5 khun3 poaN3-tiam2 bin5.” 
  Ui2-lan5 sou2 hoat-piau2 koh soa3--loh8-khi3 e5 oe7, chiu7-si7 i sou2 bat tu2-tioh8 choe3 thong3-khou2 e5 keng-giam7. Kui2-na7 e5 chheng-lian5, tak8 me5-hng lai5 kou3-siu2 i, m7-chun2 i khun3, jit8--si5 tioh8 cho3 nge7-thau5 e5 kang, chiu7-si7 ti7 sin5-sia7 lai7 e5 tiaN5-nih koah-chhau2. Kau3-giah8 ia3-sian7 koa3 thiam2-thau5, kau3 hit le2-pai3 e5 boe2-jit8, i chiu7 khi2 cheng-sin5 iN7-chong7. U7 chit8 pai2, tng cheng-sin5 teh hoat-choh e5 si5, tng7-tioh8 keng2-chhat, chiu7 iau-kiu5 in tioh8 theh8 Seng3-keng lai5 heng5 i; pang3-tiau kong2, na7 m7 theh8 lai5 heng5, i beh chhun7-si2 phah-si2 chit8-pah lang5. Keng2-chhat chit pai2 khak-sit8 u7 kiaN--tioh8. Ui7-tioh8 in e5 chan5-jim2 khoan2-thai7 i, ti3-kau3 hou7 i piN3-chiaN5 chit8 e5 gui5-hiam2 e5 siau2-lang5; in chiu7 chiong Seng3-keng theh8 lai5 heng5 i; iah8 eng7 hoat-tou7 beh lai5 tin3-cheng7 i hit tiam2 khi3. Keng-koe3 boe7 loa7-ku2, i e5 cheng-sin5 u7 hoe5-hok8, ku2-tong7 kap peng5-si5 bo5 koh-iuN7. Chong2-si7 u7-si5 chiu7 koh khi2, ia7 tui3 ka-ki7 e5 heng5-ui5 soa3 boe7-tit-thang hu7 chek-jim7. In-ui7 kiaN-kiN3 i oe7 siong-hai7 lang5, a2-si7 pang3-hoe2 sio sin5-sia7, keng2-chhat chiu7 eng7 bok8-liau7 cho3 chit8 kha toa7-toa7 kha e5 lok8-tu5 he7 ti7 in tau, ka7 i tu5--khi2-lai5. I siu7 koaiN ti7 chit kha lok8-tu5-nih chit8 ni5 ku2! Sui-jian5 hou7 lang5 khoan2-thai7 cho3 na2 chhin-chhiuN7 chit8 chiah-e5 ia2-siu3, iau2-ku2 i e5 cheng-eng u7 chiam7-chiam7 hoe5-hok8, au7-lai5 u7 siu7 pang3 chhut. Hit-tiap8 i2-au7 keng2-chhat ti7 chit8 e5 ki5-kan u7 pang3 ku3-chai7 i ka-ki7. Ui7-tioh8 i m7-bat koh hian2-chhut hiong-beng2 e5 heng5-ui5, in chiu7 siuN7 kong2 i taN piN3-chiaN5 chit8 e5 boe7 siong-hai7 lang5 e5 gong7-lang5, chiu7-si7 i2-keng bo5 cheng-sin5 e5 lang5. 
  Na7-si7 Ui2-lan5 koat-toan3 m7-si7 cheng-lek8 thoat-loh8 e5 lang5. I e5 li2-seng3 u7 hok8-goan5, tui3 ti7 cheng7-cheng7 su7-hau7 Chu2, i e5 cheng-sin5 lek8-liong7 u7 oaN7-sin; Ki-tok e5 thiaN3 noa5-chah8 i, Siong7-te3 e5 khui3-lat8 chi-chhi5 i, hou7 i oe7 thang koh chit8 pai2 lai5 ka3-si7 lang5 kap thoan5 hok-im. I bo5-lun7 kau3 sim2-mih8 sou2-chai7, ho2-taN2 ui7 Ki-tok cho3 kian3-cheng3, ti3-kau3 i e5 hoat8-tong7 u7 koh chit8 pai2 lai5 in2-khi2 keng2-chhat e5 chu3-bok8. Keng2-chhat teh giau5-gi5, siuN7 kong2 kaN2 u7 tam7-poh8 ko-san-chok8 e5 lang5 chhut-sek8 ti7 Hoe-lian5-kang2 han3-jin5 e5 kau3-hoe7-nih, chiu7 siuN7 beh ka7 in theng5-chi2. Keng2-chhat sui-jian5 teh keng2-ko3, i iah8 si7 chiap-soa3 khi3 chhut-sek8. Ti7 1944 ni5 e5 chit8 e5 le2-pai3-jit8, i ti7-hia hou7 keng2-chhat liah8-tioh8, siu7 ah-sang3 tng2-khi3 Eng-hoa-chhoan e5 keng2-chhat-sou2. 
  Keng2-tiuN2 kong2, “Li2 iu7-koh lai5 lah, ho2 ah, li2 kah m7-thiaN chhui3, kou-put-chiong tioh8 thai5 li2.” I chiu7 kio3 chit8 e5 pou7-ha7, kah i khi3 khui chit8 e5 bong7, kong2, “Chit ho7 kha-siau3 tioh8 hou7 i si2.” I hoah iau2 chit8 e5 pou7-ha7, kong2, “To, ka7 goa2 giah8--lai5.” Hit lang5 chiu7 khi3 giah8 to chhut-lai5. Keng2-tiuN2 chiu7 puih8 to chhut siu3, iah8 hoah to-bah khoaN3 u7 lai7 bo5. Che kiam2-chhai2 si7 chit8 tiuN5 e5 khiong2-hat, chong2-si7 ia7 u7 hau7-ko2 ti7-teh. Ui2-lan5 ka-ki7 iah8 sin3 choe3-au7 e5 si5-kan i2-keng kau3 lah. I chiu7 khoaN3 hit ki to, ia5 kam2-kak khak-sit8 oe7 siu7 thai5-si2. Keng2-tiuN2 kong2, “Li2 taN bo5 siN3-mia7 thang tng2-khi3 lah, li2 na7 u7 sim2-mih8 ui5-gian5 beh ka7 li2 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 kong2, chit-chun7 ka7 goa2 kong2.” 
  Ui2-lan5 long2 bo5 in3 i chit8 ku3. Keng2-tiuN2 chiu7 mng7 i, khoaN3 ui7-tioh8 sim2-mih8 ian5-kou3 sin3 Ki-tok-kau3, sin3 kau3 chiah jin7-chin? Ui2-lan5 taN2-sng3 beh ti7 choe3-au7 e5 sun3-kan ui7 sin3-giong2 cho3 kian3-cheng3, chiu7 in3 kong2, “KiN3-na7 sin3 e5 lang5 beh tit-tioh8 eng2-oan2 e5 oah8-mia7.” I chiu7 mng7 i kong2, “An2-ni li2 m7 kak-gou7 beh si2 lah?” I chiu7 eng7 chai7-ngou2, bo5 teng5-ku3 e5 siaN-tiau7 in3 kong2, “Si7, goa2 kak-gou7.” Hit-chun7 u7 chit8 e5 keng2-chhat oat8-tng2-sin, chhiN-chhiN choh8-choh8 ka7 pat8 e5 keng2-chhat kong2, “Sin3-giong2 si7 sim2-mih8? Bo5 chit8 hang7 oe7 thang io5-tang7 i.” Au7-lai5 in chiu7 pang3 i chhut--lai5, chun2 i tng2-khi3. 
  Ui2-lan5 chiap-soa3 koh ti7 soaN-kan e5 sou2-chai7 khui pi3-bit8 e5 chu7-hoe7. 1945 ni5 si3 geh8 u7 chit8 jit8, i siu7 tiau3 khi3 keng2-chhat-sou2, keng2-chhat ka7 i kong2, Lo5-su-hok Chong2-thong2 i2-keng si2, in siuN7 beh saN-kap khui chit8-tng3 ngou2-chhan lai5 kheng3-chiok i e5 si2. Leng7-goa7 iau2 u7 chit8-ui7 Eng-hoa-chhoan e5 Ki-tok-tou5 kio3-cho3 Pai-lan5 e5, ia7 hou7 in kio3 khi3. In chiu7 chiong chit8 tiuN mia5 toaN hou7 i, mia5-toaN-nih u7 khia7 gou7 e5 lang5-mia5, i tioh8 chhoa7 hit gou7 e5 lang5 khi3 hu3 kheng3-chiok-hoe7. Ui7-tioh8 hiah-e5 lang5-mia5 long2 si7 Ki-tok-tou5 e5 mia5, Pai-lan5 chiu7 ti7 sim-lai7 siuN7 kong2, KaN2-si7 u7 sim2-mih8 sou2-chai7 teh bo5 tu2-ho2, Ki-tok-tou5 long2-chong2 teh-beh khi3 siu7 keng2-chhat sim2-mng7 lah! In iau2-boe7 khi3 hu3-hoe7 e5 tai7-seng, i chiu7 tiau3-chip8 in lai5 ti7 i e5 chhu3-nih, bian2-le7 in tioh8 khia7-chai7, na7 eng3-kai si2, chiu7 si2; m7-thang pang3-sak hok-im. Tng i teh bian2-le7 in e5 si5-chun7, u7 chit8 e5 keng2-chhat jip8-lai5, hi7-hong-a2 u7 thiaN-tioh8 i sou2 kong2 e5 boe2 ku3, chiu7 khong3-ko3 in, kong2 in si7 teh ka7 Lo5 Chong2-thong2 khui tui-to7-hoe7; Ki-tok-tou5 hou2-jin7, kong2 bo5 iaN2, na7-si7 keng2-chhat m7-sin3. 
  Chit-tiap8 i2-au7 chian3-cheng e5 kiok8-se3 chai7 Jit8-pun2 e5 lip8-tiuN5 lai5 kong2, si7 kek8-ki5 am3-tam7 e5. Chai7 Tai5-oan5 e5 tong-kiok8-chia2 u7 kau3-giah8 teh u7-siong2 lian5-hap8-kun chiuN7-liok8 e5 su7. Tak8 sou2-chai7 e5 keng2-chhat chu7-jian5 u7 siu7-tioh8 beng7-leng7, kah in tioh8 ka-kiong5 kam3-si7 long2-chong2 u7 kho2-leng5-seng3 thang cho3 “te7-gou7 chhiong3-tui7 e5 lang5.” Sou2 u7 e5 Ki-tok-tou5 put-lun7 si7 han3-chok8 e5, a2-si7 ko-san-chok8 e5, long2 siu7 pau-ham5 ti7 chit lui7 e5 lai7-bin7. Chai7 Eng-hoa chhoan e5 sou2-chai7 bo5 koh-iuN7 pat8-ui7, keng2-chhat u7 ka-kin2 lai5 teh koan2-sok in. Ki-tok-tou5 e5 tiong-kan u7 kui2-na7 lang5 eng7 hoat-tou7 koh tit-tioh8 Seng3-keng. Keng2-chhat u7 iau-kiu5 chiah-e5 chheng-lian5 tioh8 pang3-sak Seng3-keng kap si-chheh, ia7 soa3 pang3-sak sin3-giong2; na7-si7 in ka7 i ku7-choat8. Keng2-chhat ui7-tioh8 ai3 chai-iaN2 chai7 chng-nih sim2-mih8 lang5 khak-sit8 si7 Ki-tok-tou5, chiu7 khai-si2 chit8 hoe5 chin thiat-te2 e5 hou7-khau2 tiau-cha. In mui2 me5-hng kiam2-cha chit8 hou7, chiong in e5 ka-chok8 sui5-e5 sui5-e5 kio3 chhut-lai5 mng7, choe3-au7 chiah chhiau in e5 chhu3. Ki-tok-tou5 keng-koe3 chit8 cham7 e5 toa7 chhi3-lian7. In u7 cheng3-sek khui ki5-to2-hoe7 lai5 ka-ki7 kian-kou3. In ki5-to2 kong2, Ng3-bang7 in oe7 thang tui3 Ki-tok chin7-tiong, chhi5-siu2 to7-li2 kau3 si2. 
  Jit8-pun2 tau5-hang5 e5 si5, tai7-ke chin hoaN-hi2. Hiah-e5 Ki-tok-tou5 chiu7 chek-si5 kong-khai lai5 chu7-hoe7, iah8 ke3-ek8 beh khi2 pai3-tng5. In bo5 liah8 khi2 ka-ki7 e5 kau3-hoe7 cho3 boan2-chiok. TaN i2-keng bo5 keng2-chhat e5 kim3-leng7 thang chou2-tong3 in, in taN oe7 thang chiong hok-im pian3 thoan5 ti7 ko-san-chok8 e5 choan5 te7-kai3. In taN oe7 thang chu7-iu5 si3-koe3 kiaN5-iu5, put-lun7 kau3 sim2-mih8 sou2-chai7 e7 thang ui7 Ki-tok choe3 kian3-cheng3. 1946 ni5 chiaN-geh8, u7 chit8 thoan5 Eng-hoa sia7 e5 Ki-tok-tou5 siu7 Ui2-lan5 e5 leng2-to7, ti7 saN li7 kui2-na7 Eng-li2 hng7 e5 chit8 e5 A-mi-chok8 e5 hiuN-sia7-nih khui pou3-to7-hoe7. Kau3 kau2-geh8 e5 si5, u7 tit-tioh8 chiah-e5 A-mi-chok8 chin-choe7 lang5 lai5 kui Ki-tok, in si7 kau3-giah8 u7 khui3-lat8 thang ui7 in pun2-sin khi2 pai3-tng5. Hit keng kau3-hoe7 si7 tok8-it bu5 ji7 e5; chiu7-si7 tui3 hiah-e5 m7-bat A-mi oe7 e5 goa7-chok8 (Thai3-ia5-chok8) e5 kang-lang5 e5 lou2-lek8 lai5 kiat-chiaN5 e5. In m7-bat A-mi oe7, sou2-i2 beh thoan5 to7-li2 hou7 in tioh8 eng7 Jit8-gu2. Put-tan3 an2-ni, chiah-e5 thoan5 to7-li2 hou7 A-mi-chok8 e5 Thai3-ia5-chok8 iah8 u7 ui7-tioh8 in pun2-sin khi2 pai3-tng5, che si7 chit8 ni5 cheng5 e5 su7 na7-tiaN7. In bo5 siu7 siat-lip8 e5 bok8-su a2-si7 siu7 koe3 hun3-lian7 e5 leng2-to7-chia2. In lian5 chit8 e5 siu7 siat-lip8 e5 tiuN2-lo2 iah8 iau2-boe7 u7, chong2-si7 in u7 oah8-oah8 e5 sin3-giong2 kap thoan5-to7 cheng-sin5. In e5 kau3-hoe7 si7 tng teh siu7 hoan2-tui3 kap pek-hai7 e5 si5 kian3-siat e5. In e5 hoe7-iu2 toa7-to-sou3 u7 tui3 iam7-iam7 e5 he2-lou5 keng-ke3, chong2-si7 bo5 tai7-chi3. 
  Keng-ke3 hit e5 ku2-ku2 e5 hoan7-lan7, khiN5-tiau5 ti7 Chu2, bo5 si5 bo5 khek eng7 sin5-leng5 e5 ui3-an teh kou2-bu2 i e5 tang5-chok8 e5, chiu7-si7 hit ui7 u7 sin3-sim e5 Ui2-lan5. I ui7-tioh8 chin-li2 cho3 kian3-cheng3 bo5 siuN7 sian7. Siu7 kong3, siu7 phah, sim7-chi3 ui7-tioh8 Ki-tok e5 ian5-kou3, cheng-sin5 khi2 iN7-chong7. I m7-goan7 ti7 chan5-jim2 bo5 tang3 sng3-khi2 e5 Jit8-pun2 e5 hoat-lut8 e7 lai5 khut-hok8 lang5. I si7 chit8 ui7 phok-sou3, lau2-sit8, kiaN-ui3 Siong7-te3 e5 peng5-siong5 lang5. I kong2-oe7 seng5-sit8, heng5-ui5 toan-chong, m7-goan7 khut-hok8 ti7 jim7-ho5 oe7 pai7-hoai7 e5 lang5 e5 bin7-cheng5; in-ui7 i siong-sin3 chi2 u7 “Ia5-sou e5 mia5 ban7 kha-thau5-u tioh8 kui7-pai3.” Ui2-lan5 kin-a2-jit8 iau2 si7 kau3-hoe7 e5 tong3-liong5, chai7 Tai5-oan5 chiah-e5 peng5-bin5 e5 thoan5-kau3-chia2 e5 tiong-kan, i sng3 si7 choe3 iu2-lek8 e5 chit8 e5. 
  Chian3-cheng au7 e5 chin3-pou7 
